image-ada (unreleased)

  * Initial release.

  * Added:
    - pnm_reader.ad{s,b}
        - a generic package to read PBM, PGM and PPM files into a grayscale raster
    - pnmread.adb
        - a program to read files supported by the pnm_reader.ad{s,b} package and to dump them as ASCII PGM images, primarily for testing the pnm_reader but also for some casual conversion ;).